    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deal 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>. If possible, consume up to 3 stacks of the target's <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bond of Life</span> and increase DMG by the same amount.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Bond of Life</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached is healed:</span> This effect will be consumed once for every <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span> it has to negate 1 HP of healing received. (Cannot negate revives or healing caused by redistribution of HP)<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">): 1</span> (Can stack, no stack limit).</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/10/35428890/8b9e6f74983ab55b4e35032ee8e5f466_607956500357611991.png",
                "id": "talent5676",
                "key": "Invitation to a Beheading",
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Invitation to a Beheading"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Create 5 stacks of <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Blood-Debt Directive</span> on the opponent's side of the field and deal 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Blood-Debt Directive</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After your character receives DMG: </span>Attach 1 stack of <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Bond of Life</span> to the character who took DMG and the opponent's Arlecchino.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 5</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/10/35428890/51dcd771e9be34b266c5d81f26692f2d_3028373041106619070.png",
                "id": "talent1385",
                "key": "All Is Ash ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "All Is Ash "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deal 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>. Remove all of your stacks of <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bond of Life</span> and heal yourself for 1 HP per stack.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Bond of Life</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached is healed:</span> This effect will be consumed once for every <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span> it has to negate 1 HP of healing received. (Cannot negate revives or healing caused by redistribution of HP)<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Can stack, no stack limit).</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/10/35428890/47325a7a24de844e24403e6fcaa25878_7903696618605869662.png",
                "id": "talent14763",
                "key": "Balemoon Rising",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Balemoon Rising"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>Characters won't receive healing from sources other than <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Balemoon Rising</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When Bond of Life is attached to self:</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> dealt by characters is converted to <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Bond of Life</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached is healed:</span> This effect will be consumed once for every <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span> it has to negate 1 HP of healing received. (Cannot negate revives or healing caused by redistribution of HP)<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Can stack, no stack limit).</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/10/35428890/6e53adea8ee6f59c6af079daaec681f8_5344638447010741103.png",
                "id": "talent64300",
                "key": "The Balemoon Alone May Know ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "The Balemoon Alone May Know "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Pyro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/10/35428890/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_924748411367884523.png",
                "id": "talent26456",
                "key": "Pyro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Pyro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/10/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_6809864920913852107.png",
                "id": "talent80340",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
